          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0669P0-02419'>
        <a name='S5LV0669P0_20050209_GCR_20'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-patricia-scotland' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0669P0_20050209_GCR_20' title='Link to this speech by Ms Patricia Scotland' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-patricia-scotland" title="Ms Patricia Scotland">Baroness Scotland of Asthal</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
