            <q>The purposes within this subsection (see subsection (2)(1))".</q>
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_98gc' title='Col. 98GC &mdash; HL Deb 09 February 2005 vol 669 c98GC' name='column_98gc' href='#column_98gc' rel='bookmark'>98GC</a>
