            <q>the law relating to charities in England and Wales",</q>
            is not altered by the inclusion of the words "from time to time". Therefore, we do not believe it is necessary to include the words "from time to time", although I absolutely understand that the noble Lord wanted me to have an opportunity to confirm that what he would most wish to happen will be the case. I am more than happy to do that.
